reviews.review_text: Always good service here. Our fav location that close to our house. Happy meal and fish burger are our fav that always order. Oh! Also like their Boston cream donut that not too sweet and just perfect size for me when Im craving for treat

I have been to so many McDonald s, this is by far the best of best   so clean, staff very kind and professional. The food omg fresh!! I bet this is what McDonald s tasted like when it first open  I am McDonald s addict. This just cures my craving with its delicious and fresh Big Mac with large fries without salt, and refreshing Coca Cola. Thank you so much keep the great job going.

I just want to give a big shout out to your manager working at this location named Preet. I had an error on my order, and when I came back days later, and she remembered exactly who I was even without me, mentioning it and made everything right !

As I rolled in today it quite busy but yet the delivery was fast. I m amazed as how the workers can work in this heat. A round of applause to these workers and hope their family are well. I would like to thank all of these workers as it s not an easy job. So grateful to have these kind folks in my community and will forever be. Thank you McDonald s as I owe you a big one.
Thank you for great service. Staff always accommodating and good food!

Today was a dark and cloudy day where the only promise for the day was that it was going to rain. I had just finished at the dentist when I decided that I NEEDED a Diet Coke from McDonalds (Panorama, Surrey) I drove thru, gave my order and went to the window to pay.  There was a young girl who was laughing and smiling as she passed me my drink.  She asked me if I would be willing to give a review of my visit.  I said yes, I promise!  Her cheerfulness made me smile and the rest of the day seemed better  .sometimes you just need someone to give you their smile.  Thank you and I will stop through again when I m in the neighbourhood!!   Sharon
Great place . Located at very convenient location

It was the best we got free FOod and extra stuff cause they thought the card payment got through and someone else had a very similar i order to us so they thought we ordered the other persons order (also this was a few years ago so dont try to get free food and stuff so like yAsSs) Also sLaY

Great customer service by the entire team , it was late and they had closed the store only drive through was open. I placed order and went walking to pay. They helped me wait in the store for my order. I had walked long distance and got cold water and my order was delivered quickly. Thank you
Service was amazing and very minimal waiting time for delivery

I want to start off by saying, I have experience dining at fast food restaurants throughout my college and university years. The Panorama location, in my opinion is not only the most pleasant McDonalds location that I have experience but the most pleasant fast food restaurant that I know of. The staff is super friendly and the location is very clean on a consistent basis. The manager working, Earin has an excellent attitude and I can see she leads her entire staff by example. I eat here often and there are times when its busy and the manager keeps her cool and you can see the confidence in her and her team. I also see that the organization takes their customers serious by their recognition of adding a better drive through. Overall, I think I speak for alot of others when I say, this McDonalds location is a great part of the community and the people that work here should be recognized for their efforts. Especially the management team. Thanks. Roy

Every work morning when theres no line up its nice to stop by and pick up a tea. Its become so routine I believe theyve remembered my order and Ive enjoyed the attention they take in recognizing that in their busy day. Theres also a nice lady who makes the best iced coffee.

The staff on breakfast shift 6:45 am very friendly and acomedating to my friend who is a celiac, girl at the till was very good made sure my order was done right, she handled things like a boss showed she cares, I m coming back! Dietary restrictions: McDonalds needs to provide gluten free options to be more accomedating Parking: Good parking. Next to restraunt
I have always had a very good experience at this McDonalds. Theyre very, very clean and super accommodating 10 out of 10.
Fries were hot!!! Cant tell you how many McDonalds Ive been to and the fries were cold. There was no lineup and service was quick. Food was brought out to our car quickly and everything was warm.
If you want the best experience ever, go in the morning. You will meet the best polite people ever. Dont know the young team that helped me s name but they are amazing!
Nice drive threw and hot fries nice ty
Very convenient self order screen, normally not so busy, restaurant is always clean and well kept.

Alright, so I know this is just another McDonalds, but the staff here is incredible. Service is kind, prompt, and accurate. Ive never had a bad experience here. I most often drive through however the odd time I have used the dining room the staff has been so helpful and accommodating to this mom with 3 small kids.

Best Mcdonalds I have ever been to , mostly because they are very fast but really reliable.  Food tastes fresh and the staff is friendly.  Especially the managers, one time they charged me full price when I had a coupon but with covid they never ask to see them, but now things are back to normal I need to show them.  I called back to get the coupon price and they replaced the whole meal and gave me complimentary apple pies :) never thought I would write a review for a Mcdonalds but this place rocks.  They make the Mcdoubles perfect XD and the staff is so polite!  The managers have set a great example to follow as I learned during my ecperience :)  They all deserve a pizza party or something XD cant go to any other mcdonalds now because i swear they keep there food more fresh and they have the fastest service ive ever seen!
High food prices for breakfast but a good quiet place to meet with friends.

Great food and service. Nice restaurant to eat at. A big thank you to the staff for hanging onto my lava lamp for me when I accidently left it there. We got to pick it up through the drive-through since the restaurant was closed.

Love this establishment! We always custom order and they always get it correct and it tastes fresh, hot and delicious every time. Credit needs to be given to this one, they may take a little longer but atleast it seems to be made fresh and we re happy to wait! Keep up the good work guys don t let them push you into rushing and ruining orders

Amazing approach and access. The location is very conveniently located. The location is old, but the service is usually good. I like their curbside pickup a lot. The drive-in lineup at times spills over to the road.
Very nice employees on tonight...and food was good and fresh but having to wait way to long for them to bring food.
As always my kids favorite place and they always order hot cakes, fish fillet burgers and cold coffee every Saturday and Sunday. They love this place.
Quick service. Very typical McDonalds

Awesome customer service experience. The manager Param and preet delivered great customer service and made sure they made my replacement order right. I felt very welcomed. It was worth my time and money to stop by here. Thank you

This location is organized and they strive hard to deliver the fast food accurately. I saw manager making sure the correctness of the order servered. They also support people with disabilities, salute to this management and ownership.

The service at McDonalds on no 10 hwy and 152nd. is above average .I have been going there for over 10 years and have Never had to complain about anything. Sandra is a super star. ALWAYS doing her very best to keep the restaurant in top shape.Cleaning continually, fast service, pleasant, ALWAYS trying to keep the customers happy and welcome.Parm and Darcy are also excellent..This location is the best. There are other staff who try very hard including the very professional and hardworking Kuldip the manager...It doesnt get any better than this location..they understand what great service means. Brian Wilson
Best Fast food in the kanada

The cashier was new so she was missing details here and there, however, a lovely experienced old lady was constantly overlooking the new staff and constantly checking with customer.  Never had such nice dinning experience in other McDonalds.
Fast service and good food. Customer service can be better,  nice to hear and have a smile on employees faces.  Seems like the guy was forced to be in there.

Just this evening between 5-7PM (not sure) March 24th, 2020, I had two separate issues with my McNugget and Big Mac. Manager Parm and her team were very professional and swift to help me deal with my issues. With the current pandemic going on, it s understandable if the staffs were as stressed as customers like me, but all of them treated me with care and respect, which I appreciate very much and want to let people know about it. This is my first time having issues with McDonald s in general, but isn t the first time I experienced high level of attention and care from the staffs of this McDonald s location. From other places, I experienced and understood there s always a certain SOP to satisfy (upset) customers and handle situations like this, but the professional and careful attitudes makes all the difference. Whoever s reading this comment; wether you are from regional management or local staff, as long as you are related to this McDonald s location, I want you to know, the neighborhood and I appreciate you and your hard work very much. Sincerely, -Ian, the guy with face mask.
Mehec was so kind when we arrived here. She welcomes us so kindly and lovely I love you visit here after school
Okay so this has got to be one of the best mcdonalds I have been to for customer service especially the young man at the window who took my order great job everyone keep up the good work
Fast service, affordable food, clean location and friendly staff.
I had the best McDonald s at this location yesterday   the buns were fresh and the patties were more juicy compared to any other locations I ve tried before. It was rather random haha.
I stop in here on a 5 day daily basis, the food is always fresh, I get it very quickly and the place is spotlessly clean, very, very friendly staff as well. Very well managed.

Went in for a quick snack and ordered a couple of ice cream for the grand daughters... The girls eyes popped when they seen the generous helping of ice cream... And a cup of extra ice cream in a cup with a spoon...we will definitely be returning...

Friendly greeter upon entering, brings your order to your table and if you need anything else and promptly removing the tray when finished.   The only Macdonald Restaurant I have been to that has a greeter.
My daughter loved the inside play place. The staff is great and I can request my food be delivered to my table anywhere in the restaurant, even the kids play place.
My last visit was through a curb side pick up and my order was 100% accurate and fresh!!! Thanks a lot !!! Great Job  !!!
Their coffee was very Authentic and true to McDonalds taste. Staff was happy and attentive. Full marks..
A quiet place for a dinner! They had a few customers, but the drive in were really a long line of customers!
I go there every morning to get an egg macmuffin for my 92 year old mother. Staff are great and some even say my name when going through the drive through and high to my dog rocky
